: 3241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8791075137729838e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free metro tickets\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beloved public spaces like the famed Pompidou Centre are now clogged up with tawdry sports commercialism, with Nike ads blazing on the building's storied facade like a Las Vegas casino.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9836995785899451, \"rank\": 0.01657052799930212, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"score\": 0.9976861374977712, \"rank\": 0.0023192288748676406, \"text\": \"Las Vegas\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Las_Vegas_Strip\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Beloved public spaces\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"the famed Pompidou Centre\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"tawdry sports commercialism\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3461}, {\"ngram\": \"the building's storied facade\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon seeing this, one social media user, in a paroxysm of extreme Frenchness,posted\\\"I have no words in the face of such horror.\\\"\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one social media user\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3582}, {\"ngram\": \"a paroxysm\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme Frenchness\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"posted\\\"I\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"no words\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3642}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"such horror\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the unions of Paris have not rolled over.\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3691, \"end\": 3696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8791075137729838e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unions\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Games approached, worker power has leveraged the once-in-a-generation opportunity to score wage hikes.\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3731}, {\"ngram\": \"worker power\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"a-generation\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3795}, {\"ngram\": \"wage hikes\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Garbage collectors, train drivers, air-traffic controllers, and police are using their leverage to demand Olympic bonuses.\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Garbage collectors\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3847}, {\"ngram\": \"train drivers\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"air-traffic controllers\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3887}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"their leverage\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic bonuses\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, with the opening ceremony slated for Friday, the SFA-CGT union representing around 10 percent of the dancers in the kick-off eventfileda strike notice over \\\"outrageous disparities\\\" in pay between performers.\", \"from\": 3952, \"to\": 4164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 3994, \"to\": 4000}, {\"ngram\": \"the SFA-CGT union\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"around 10 percent\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4050}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancers\", \"from\": 4054, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"the kick-off eventfileda strike notice\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4107}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"outrageous disparities\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"pay\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4144}, {\"ngram\": \"performers\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The political issues on display are not limited merely to the Parisian.\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The political issues\", \"from\": 4166, \"to\": 4186}, {\"ngram\": \"display\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4197}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisian\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Justice for Palestine and anger at the inclusion of Israeli Olympians, which we will surely write more upon in the days ahead, is very much on display.\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4250, \"end\": 4259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"score\": 0.9996891921703053, \"rank\": 0.0003109041146979447, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_of_Palestine\"}, {\"begin\": 4290, \"end\": 4297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9995252926747237, \"rank\": 0.0004749310120736559, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Justice\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4245}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 