now things are getting real.\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5311, \"to\": 5317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And French soldiers are posted around the city to remind you of this almost surreal reality.\", \"from\": 5336, \"to\": 5428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5340, \"end\": 5346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9731020808717722, \"rank\": 0.024830221659780435, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 5374, \"to\": 5382}, {\"ngram\": \"this almost surreal reality\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will be in Paris to follow the off-the-field machinations forThe Nation, so stay tuned.\", \"from\": 5429, \"to\": 5519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5443, \"end\": 5448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8791075137729838e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the-field\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5476}, {\"ngram\": \"Nation\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A big thank you to Garry Whannel for letting us use his flat asThe Nation's Paris headquarters for the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 5521, \"to\": 5638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5597, \"end\": 5602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8791075137729838e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Garry Whannel\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5553}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 5566, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even before February 28, the reasons for Donald Trump's imploding approval rating were abundantly clear: untrammeled corruption and personal enrichment to the tune of billions of dollars during an affordability crisis, a foreign policy guided only by his own derelict sense of morality, and the deployment of a murderous campaign of occupation, detention, and deportation on American streets.\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 6032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5681, \"end\": 5693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999984383976, \"rank\": 1.5612987843303837e-09, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 6015, \"end\": 6023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.087173565427562e-16, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 5652, \"to\": 5660}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5676}, {\"ngram\": \"untrammeled corruption\", \"from\": 5745, \"to\": 5767}, {\"ngram\": \"personal enrichment\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5791}, {\"ngram\": \"the tune\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5803}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 5807, \"to\": 5815}, {\"ngram\": \"dollars\", \"from\": 5819, \"to\": 5826}, {\"ngram\": \"an affordability crisis\", \"from\": 5834, \"to\": 5857}, {\"ngram\": \"a foreign policy\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5875}, {\"ngram\": \"his own derelict sense\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5913}, {\"ngram\": \"morality\", \"from\": 5917, \"to\": 5925}, {\"ngram\": \"the deployment\", \"from\": 5931, \"to\": 5945}, {\"ngram\": \"a murderous campaign\", \"from\": 5949, \"to\": 5969}, {\"ngram\": \"occupation\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5983}, {\"ngram\": \"detention\", \"from\": 5985, \"to\": 5994}, {\"ngram\": \"deportation\", \"from\": 6000, \"to\": 6011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now an undeclared, unauthorized, unpopular, and unconstitutional war of aggression against Iran has spread like wildfire through the region and into Europe.\", \"from\": 6034, \"to\": 6190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6125, \"end\": 6129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9999986507309594, \"rank\": 7.272872723632278e-07, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an undeclared, unauthorized, unpopular, and unconstitutional war\", \"from\": 6038, \"to\": 6102}, {\"ngram\": \"aggression\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6116}, {\"ngram\": \"wildfire\", \"from\": 6146, \"to\": 6154}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 6163, \"to\": 6173}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 6183, \"to\": 6189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new \\\"forever war\\\"-with an ever-increasing likelihood of American troops on the ground-may very well be upon us.\", \"from\": 6191, \"to\": 6304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6249, \"end\": 6257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.087173565427562e-16, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ever-increasing likelihood\", \"from\": 6216, \"to\": 6245}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 6268, \"to\": 6278}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6301, \"to\": 6303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we have seen over and over, this administration uses lies, misdirection, and attempts to flood the zone to justify its abuses of power at home and abroad.\", \"from\": 6306, \"to\": 6463, \"entities\": [], \"nou